{{Reactor}}
== Overview ==
The Quantum Syncron utilizes the 'multiverse' to store amazing levels of stored power in an alternative space dimensions. Like all [[Quantum|Quantum reactors]] the charging process is provided externally and the purpose of the reactor is to provide unequalled deflection against power attacks.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Quantum Syncron Reactor can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in Vulcore.

